posts.post_content:
I've been stubbornly refusing to get involved with t205 or t206 oddities up until now, but I'm begining to relent a little bit and thought I'd see what t205s are out there that people may be willing to unload.  I'm interested in wet-sheet transfers, handcut examples, double prints, severe miscuts, missing borders, missing color passes, etc...etc..

Paying well and condition/player is no concern to me.  Thanks in advance!

Brian
